parameters: The darkest darkness shall devour you otherwise.
もう動かす必要はないでしょう。
This is the only room that is still dark.
Gee, we've been warned plenty, huh?
The true darkness will consume you,
Rather, I welcome them to try me.
You're really filled with courage today...
If that's what you want, then let it be so.
What, it's just a Shadow Monster.
I knew it from the beginning.
I couldn't sense the influence of darkness
Seriously, why did you do that?
It seems comfortable for Shadow Monsters.
I don't know why this place was closed down,
but it seems to work out your way.
Even though you already knew, Ino,
why come all the way here?
Well, I wanted to get revenge.
You scared me silly, after all.
To frighten us who dwell in the dark, despite
Oi, you there. What's your name?
